*Acceptance Criteria* *_(focus on the what, not the how)_*

* Users allocated to {{Control}} 
** should not see the Feeding Plan Type question on /plans quiz page
** should see the 4 plan cards as BAU without any portion percentage selectors 
* Users allocated to {{variation_1}}
** should see the Feeding Plan Type question on /plans quiz page
** should see only 3 plans (cards)
** for answer {{full}}*_, should not see portion percentage options and user should be defaulted to 100% SKU_*
** for answer {{mix}} *_, should see portion percentage options and have the lowest portion percentage option selected by default on each plan_*
** for answer {{not sure}}*_, should have the  100% option selected by default on each plan_*
* Users allocated to {{variation_2}}
** should see the Feeding Plan Type question on /plans quiz page
** should see only 3 plans (cards)
** for answer {{full}}*_, should not see portion percentage options and user should be defaulted to 100% SKU_*
** for answers {{mix}} and {{not sure}}, *_should have the  100% option selected by default on each plan_*
