*Developer Information* 

* Sine {{useStarterAllPortionedProductOffers}} is responsible for filtering the options through {{getAllowedPortionsForCalories}}. We can create a similar function as {{getAllowedPortionsForFunnel}}, with the filtering required for funnel pages and invoke it instead of the current function which will be used only for the Active user‚Äôs non funnel flows
** [https://github.com/hellofresh/web/blob/master/app/spaces/whitelabel/modules/whitelabel-web/packages/components/plans-selection/data/useProductOffers.ts#L109|https://github.com/hellofresh/web/blob/master/app/spaces/whitelabel/modules/whitelabel-web/packages/components/plans-selection/data/useProductOffers.ts#L109] 

{noformat}```typescript
export const getAllowedPortionsForFunnel = (calories?: number): number[] => {
  if (!calories || Number.isNaN(calories)) {
    return [50, 100];
  }
  if (calories >= 89 && calories <= 149) return [100];
  if (calories >= 150 && calories <= 225) return [75, 100];
  return [50, 100];  // NO 75% for 226+
};
```{noformat}
